-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die <strong><code>Navigator.vibrate()</code></strong>-Methode erzeugt eine Vibration, wenn entsprechende Hardware vorhanden ist. Wenn das Gerät keine Vibration unterstützt, hat diese Methode keine Auswirkungen. Wenn eine Vibration gestartet werden soll, aber eine andere Vibration noch ausgeführt wird, wird die Alte gestoppt und die Neue gestartet!</p>\n\n<p>Wenn die Methode nicht ausgeführt werden konnte aufgrund eines ungültigen Parameters wird ein <em>false </em>zurückgegeben, ansonsten ein <em>true</em>. Wenn das Modell zu lang ausgeführt wird, wird es abgeschnitten: die maximale Dauer ist je nach Implementierung abhängig!</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var <em>successBool</em> = window.navigator.vibrate(<em><var>pattern</var></em>);\n</pre>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"pattern\"><em>pattern</em></dt>\n <dd>Bietet ein Schema von Vibrationen und Vibrationsintervallen. Jeder Wert bezeichnet eine Anzahl an Millisekunden zum vibrieren und pausieren (im Wechsel). <span id=\"result_box\" lang=\"de\"><span>Sie</span> <span>bieten</span> <span>entweder einen einzelnen</span> <span>Wert</span> <span>(um einmal</span> <span>für so viele</span> <span>Millisekunden</span> <span>zu vibrieren</span><span>)</span> <span>oder</span> <span>ein Array von Werten</span><span>, um abwechselnd</span> zu <span>vibrieren</span><span>,</span> pausieren<span>, dann</span> <span>wieder</span> <span>zu vibrieren.</span> </span> Siehe <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Vibration_API\" title=\"/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Vibration\">Vibration API</a> für weitere Details.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Wenn man 0 als Wert, einen leeren Array oder einen Array, der nur 0 als Wert(e) enthält, angibt wird die Vibration gestoppt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vibrate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// vibriert 200ms lang</span>\nwindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vibrate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">30</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// vibriert 'SOS' im Morsecode</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technische_daten","title":"Technische Daten","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Technische Daten</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Hinweis</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/2009/dap/vibration/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'Vibration API' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">Vibration API</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Empfehlung</span></td>\n   <td>Linked to spec is the latest editor's draft; W3C version is a REC.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser-kompatibilität","title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funktion</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span> <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/11\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2012-03-13.\">11.0</a> (11.0) <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">moz (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/16\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2012-10-09.\">16.0</a> (16.0) (no prefix) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Funktion</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Grundlegende Unterstützung</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span> <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td>11.0 (11.0) <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">moz (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    16.0 (16.0) (no prefix) [1]</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p>[1] Wenn die Vibration zulang ist, das heißt der Wert selbst oder das Muster, wurde bis einschließlich Firefox 26 anstatt&nbsp; <code>false</code>, eine Fehlermeldung zurückgegeben (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=884935\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;884935</a>). Ab Firefox 32 wird <code>true</code> zurückgegeben, aber das Muster gekürzt (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1014581\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug&nbsp;1014581</a>).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"weitere_informationen","title":"Weitere Informationen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Vibration_API\" title=\"/en-US/docs/WebAPI/Vibration\">Vibration API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Technische Daten","id":"technische_daten"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Weitere Informationen","id":"weitere_informationen"}],"summary":"Die Navigator.vibrate()-Methode erzeugt eine Vibration, wenn entsprechende Hardware vorhanden ist. Wenn das Gerät keine Vibration unterstützt, hat diese Methode keine Auswirkungen. Wenn eine Vibration gestartet werden soll, aber eine andere Vibration noch ausgeführt wird, wird die Alte gestoppt und die Neue gestartet!","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Navigator.vibrate()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.navigator.vibrate","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Navigator.vibrate()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Navigator.vibrate()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Navigator.vibrate()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Navigator.vibrate()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/navigator/vibrate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/navigator/vibrate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator","title":"Navigator"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Navigator/vibrate","title":"Navigator.vibrate()"}],"pageTitle":"Navigator.vibrate() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}